trans-unit.source: Represents a table in a document.

A TableStructure can be a child of any of these document structure elements: - <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragment> - <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.SectionStructure> - <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure> (when the table is nested in an outer table) - <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.ListItemStructure>
trans-unit.target: TableStructure 可以是任何这些文档结构元素的子级:- <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragment>- <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.SectionStructure>- <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure>（时表嵌套在外部表）- <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.ListItemStructure></xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.ListItemStructure> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.SectionStructure> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragment>
